Tight integration for mpich-1 was tested with version
mpich-1.2.6.

Building mpich
==============
When you build mpich, make sure to configure mpich to use rsh (without path)
as rsh command:
configure -rsh=rsh --prefix=...

Installing the PE
=================
qconf -Ap $SGE_ROOT/mpi/mpich/mpich.template
